      <title>新加坡建筑商 Oxley 寻求高达 1.2 亿美元的私人贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/singapore-builder-oxley-seeks-up-to-120-million-private-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，资金短缺的新加坡房地产开发商豪利控股有限公司 (Oxley Holdings Ltd) 正在寻求 1 亿至 1.2 亿美元的私人信贷贷款，部分用于帮助偿还下个月到期的新加坡元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/singapore-builder-oxley-seeks-up-to-120-million-private-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 01:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
